<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.10.4">
<l>ēṟu mēṟiyi laṅkumoṇ maḻup paṟṟu mīcaṟki caintuṭam pilōr</l>
<l>kūṟu tāṉkoṭut tāṉkula māmakaṭ kiṉiyāṉ</l>
<l>nāṟu caṇpaka mallikai malar pulki yiṉṉiḷa vaṇṭunaṉ ṉaṟun</l>
<l>tēṟal vāymaṭuk kuntiruk kōṭṭiyū rāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The sweet[heart] of the great clan goddess,</l>
<l rend="indent">the one who gave a portion of [his] body,</l>
<l>Uniting to Īśa who holds a shining bright axe, riding a bull,</l>
<l>Is the one in Tirukkōṭṭiyūr where sweet little bees fill their mouths</l>
<l>With fine scented nectar, embracing fragrant champaka [and] jasmine flowers.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
